  "id": "a79d766bedcb0b9fa2e3dafe",
  "title": "Tapapakanga Regional Park",
  "summary": "又来这里最喜欢的Regional Park。 工作日的下午，一个人都没有。 牛在跟我打招呼。 羊也跟我打招呼。 […]",
  "content": "<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_9_9f674e2c-acc1-49c4-b4d8-86dbc8b61ff9.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>又来这里最喜欢的Regional Park。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_8_9f674e25-bca8-43e4-be67-b3095160dd9a-1.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>工作日的下午，一个人都没有。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"575\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_4_9f674df9-22b3-4073-aff1-30a16fa40b52.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>牛在跟我打招呼。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"575\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_1_9f674df8-f4e5-40fe-a862-d12887e86177.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>羊也跟我打招呼。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_6_9f674e21-be94-4b7c-9873-4f065f212e36.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>山顶一边是海。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"575\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_5_9f674e0f-0141-494b-a7c8-e6f7afa9e2d3.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>另一边是农场和山。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"575\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_7_9f674e27-48a4-47d3-b2a7-ab556dc2cb96.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>山上的阴影很有节奏。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"575\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_3_9f674df9-7cba-4eb5-b88e-faa8f30ec9de.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>这次来一条船都没有。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_10_9f674e35-6b95-441f-bfab-715287cbe6d8.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>跟小羊说再见啦。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"575\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_2_9f674e0f-204e-4df0-8ec5-8411272bed77.jpg?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>",
  "image": "https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/imgi_9_9f674e2c-acc1-49c4-b4d8-86dbc8b61ff9.jpg",
  "publishedAt": "2025-07-20T22:16:18Z",
  "sourceId": "a64fac5b0b6a1cd4",
  "sourceTitle": "摄影流水账",
